    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "The magic-infused metal of this bullet's golden casing allows it to curve just a bit in flight once the bullet has been fired, allowing you to ignore the bonus to AC granted to a target in lesser cover.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
